<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spy_fiction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.SpyWise.net" class="external text" title="http://www.SpyWise.net" rel="nofollow">Spy-Wise</a> The official website of Wesley A. Britton, author of three books on the fictional spy genre in print, on film and television. Contains extensive material on all aspects of spy fiction, interviews with actors, writers and producers and behind-the-scenes glimpses into the world of fictional spies.</li>
</ul>


